{"tid":676055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又入波) 警員涉虛報資料 5度騙警隊「遮仔會」共逾71萬","createTime":"2018-05-24T05:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T05:37:20.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68aa0685a6e87a67706841fcec2eb33a973517b2","tid":676055,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/209bcd010800b3489ac10d8bf8809891/tenor.gif?itemid=5168106\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F209bcd010800b3489ac10d8bf8809891%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D5168106&h=7c7dee67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又入波</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n警員涉虛報資料 5度騙警隊「遮仔會」共逾71萬<br />\n<br />\n警員於2013年至2016年期間，五次向警察儲蓄互助社(俗稱「遮仔會」)申請貸款時涉嫌虛報資料，令對方多年間共向他批出逾71萬元貸款。警員被控5項企圖欺詐罪，今在粉嶺裁判處提堂。<br />\n<br />\n現已停職的34歲警員陳曉健今由懲教人員押解上庭。辯方申請暫時毋須答辯，以待索取文件及諮詢法律意見。裁判官將案押後至7月5日再提堂，被告沒有申請保釋，期間繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號:FLCC2270/18】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180524/58230958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230958&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=ab2748c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230958&h=4b54c3f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180524/58230958</a>"},{"pid":"565281696d506d1b637b8f8c65e6019ca47b3881","tid":676055,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9G